567
00:43:40,327 --> 00:43:41,453
But Father.

568
00:43:41,453 --> 00:43:44,957
Gobernadorcillo Flores
is too old for Maria.

569
00:43:44,957 --> 00:43:46,625
They're the same age as Natasha!

570
00:43:46,750 --> 00:43:48,711
