574
00:44:04,059 --> 00:44:06,353
Since you've been spending time with...

575
00:44:07,438 --> 00:44:08,474
That woman.

576
00:44:09,773 --> 00:44:11,358
You completely changed.

577
00:44:13,694 --> 00:44:16,238
