579
00:44:18,198 --> 00:44:19,283
Stop it.

580
00:44:19,742 --> 00:44:21,535
Show respect to the Reverend Mother!

581
00:44:23,495 --> 00:44:24,580
Don Alejandro.

582
00:44:25,831 --> 00:44:28,000
It's not up to you to decide
the outcome of things.

583
00:44:29,209 --> 00:44:30,294
Keep in mind that

584
00:44:30,586 --> 00:44:34,465
your desire for wealth and power...

585
00:44:35,174 --> 00:44:38,260
comes at a great price you wouldn't expect.

586
00:44:40,637 --> 00:44:43,515
You have no right to speak to me that way.

587
00:44:52,274 --> 00:44:53,317
From now on,

588
00:44:54,276 --> 00:44:57,821
you are forbidden to be with that woman!

589
00:44:57,821 --> 00:45:00,157
But Mother Olivia has
nothing to do with this!

590
00:45:00,157 --> 00:45:04,536
