597
00:45:25,557 --> 00:45:26,266
Father!

598
00:45:26,266 --> 00:45:27,393
Father, please.

599
00:45:27,768 --> 00:45:29,978
Please try to understand Carmelita.

600
00:45:33,065 --> 00:45:34,650
This child has to be punished!

601
00:45:34,650 --> 00:45:38,404
Let her kneel on salt until I say
that she can return to her bedroom!

602
00:45:38,404 --> 00:45:39,427
