hide her far away.

625
00:46:49,850 --> 00:46:51,477
Take that old man to prison!

626
00:46:52,060 --> 00:46:53,061
I swear.

627
00:46:53,086 --> 00:46:55,254
I will make you pay,
Alejandro!

628
00:46:55,606 --> 00:46:56,623
Maria,

629
00:46:56,648 --> 00:46:57,692
it's me.

630
00:46:57,941 --> 00:46:58,775
How are you?

631
00:46:58,775 --> 00:47:00,736
